{"h97c2b79ag2e5ag4272g9ab4g898a75460306": ["Doing the rounds, are you? You'd better get some rest.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "b63dfd30-a6de-1f39-120c-1aaef0201249"], "h7167f899g19a8g46d6gaff8g17f7cd1f3ab1": ["What were you two talking about?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "962e31cb-2a6a-dc22-c840-8aeda3590809"], "h00c9990ag9903g445bg90e6g85e1d97a1839": ["What were you two talking about?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "e9e5b9f7-336c-211c-c863-4098f4978e54"], "h4cf08c6agb396g48d8ga5a4g8a56c68e47a0": ["What do you mean?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "7491d626-a6b8-6d80-2bd5-21f1cda57250"], "h8b5cf527g6593g4487gb593ge215476b3397": ["You and that Githyanki.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "217d4236-b54c-183e-4b55-2ae64bfc8bb6"], "ha664d421gff00g4979gb30ag9ecc223da31f": ["No, you've lost me. No idea what you're talking about.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "435506c7-56e5-8425-b488-4f06f82cd1e6"], "h91695867gf235g45b8gbf10gd986079fc9e4": ["Fine. Just don't expect my confidence if I don't have yours.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "afbf6ea8-aae2-01c5-4d82-ce20050836da"], "h580ebc80gb8f9g465ag9b8ag672802e6257a": ["You and Wyll.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "9bbc60af-e909-0eb4-01b6-588c065e403b"], "h6db7185dg64f1g4426gbb23gd4d1edfdb8b8": ["You and the pale fellow.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "65540564-b63b-3034-7574-e337e0ec1049"], "ha4f7aa4bge7d8g42b5g8c21ge961c41689ad": ["You and Gale.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "277b0f6d-6124-fad3-8fd2-131c165593a1"], "hfda6853cg39e1g4e90gabe7g21f08bc88ca3": ["Don't play the fool, please.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "97546036-03d8-09c8-bc94-289056ab41a2"], "h2519a10fg2e1fg4ed6g8d2dgd1a4c274fce4": ["If that was any of your business, we'd have called you over.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "e6be07de-f7f6-86e4-352f-ea819047b3fe"], "hcca510bcgd5ffg48b8gb34bg1f12415d5315": ["Wrong. Your business is mine. We're entwined, thanks to <i>this</i>. ", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "7d3a5672-ea2c-3bbb-cfc2-2c739743a4e6"], "h251bf9a4g61cbg44bdg9cc4g0653e16e0305": ["If we're to survive, we need to trust each other.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "216376c0-a16c-b9ca-c604-f7cebbcdb099"], "hf554285fg58dag46c1g8e23g6be4aa62ef9d": ["You seem reliable. I think you know how important it is that we find someone who can cure us. Best if we focus on that.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "f3e147cb-2ebe-58b8-380d-5bc37a57d5a0"], "h9cf93e66gd8f1g4118g8b69gf17f409e7790": ["And just to be clear, come daybreak, finding a healer is our first priority.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "e2b0268c-d393-c62e-481c-b06e47082540"], "haee2aa4fg6afbg4061gb7e9g9644c7cad6e0": ["Agreed. The sooner we find someone to help us, the better.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "6675051c-c21d-d0a9-91f3-8704bc97b715"], "h94db9a27g9994g4977g94eag35ec0bc2d3c5": ["Good. We might even get lucky and find one right away. As I see it, we're overdue some good fortune. Rest well.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "62a5cd9a-6ae2-5d0d-0f63-8a441475f2f6"], "h89643509gdc7bg4d90gae49g67866076e266": ["It's late. We can talk about this in the morning.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "19a3db66-90a8-ed9c-16ee-2e18a7df3a8e"], "h6dc13dc4gb090g4071g9a91gdba2d09eedd4": ["We did just talk about it. Let's rest.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "2a57f4b0-b03c-f974-4d9a-b91534783b20"], "h1b15ce96g6c53g4a12gba71ga1d7ec49e231": ["Let's not abandon all caution. This is unfamiliar territory.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "cc724970-4d68-ac0a-b605-98e26c90e32c"], "h150b40d1g8302g4a2bg9bf9g4bfac1be4940": ["Caution is a luxury we don't have. Let's rest and wake up at first light.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "d4c64a74-b1c5-f8df-18f4-4059aae711db"], "hb0e859e5g3e8dg45ffgabd0ga652d055de63": ["This isn't all bad. The tadpoles seem to have given us powers.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "04f3237b-e181-9209-95ab-4d0b74f8849d"], "hcfcc363dg3b02g459eg889fga7560161a4ed": ["These powers must have a price. They come from invasive parasites that will turn us into mind flayers.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "622b03fa-04a0-c6fd-8832-ba31b826badb"], "h1e832a96g8de3g428aga73fg08ec6c6bc97e": ["We need to get rid of them.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "98da10ea-752f-5255-aa9b-73c2937ac5bc"], "he5f5c2b7g816ag4af5ga2c6g5018472ac88e": ["Rest well. We'll need our strength.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "04733b97-8599-77ec-ffef-f2d1668f0f50"], "h7cf73b58gf2a5g4631g9a74g2bcdba594c2f": ["We were just discussing the next steps. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "2b556b86-b67f-eef8-1902-2f915d7ff816"], "h6d4f48f3gcb05g4a7dga655ge1a7cdcce760": ["I see.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "039c2aee-2004-d2f6-527d-ed833628f915"], "hd2ff133bg553cg41b1g97d2gb83934d064dc": ["I'd be careful with Lae'zel.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "d9db514d-e336-c858-c5e2-30c7e523c061"], "h71d7c428g6facg4f8cga6f1gd3a6449c6805": ["You don't trust Lae'zel?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "1cdd0736-99c7-8bf4-e80b-e7b0755cd21b"], "h163f2aeag04d3g4473gb3a2g2302e6ab0e50": ["She's not of this world. I'd be surprised if our interests remained aligned.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "2af841a1-f343-2451-1615-24656f411207"], "h0d9e5885g6916g41a4g9e98g961d727e8aab": ["Let's hope we rapidly find a healer.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "ddfd08aa-d7e9-e08f-bd61-beb9aad835ed"], "h215a929bgc2d4g4e99gab29g4fbdc82b36ea": ["You like to stir things up, don't you? Stop looking for trouble and stay focused.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "4fe32fa5-277f-c8ff-ab43-836b810c8d63"], "h379e6827g2db6g47bcg962bg737dc84b8f14": ["I was merely making an observation. ", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "cded8537-da32-74cf-2ef8-7848d2d38049"], "h452e3befg3d99g4497g94cfgaf1508708cff": ["... but speaking of focus, let's be clear: come daybreak, finding a healer is our first priority, yes?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "48fd9535-230a-7f66-432e-024f6bf28998"], "h5166070dge606g4163g8e69ga16ba4e1dd75": ["I wasn't confiding in anyone. I was just talking.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "5cc6a94b-d4fe-523c-8c2a-b981e425ab0e"], "h99ba6bddgfa8ag42c5g98ddg3ec9001ea692": ["So am I.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "a62f3862-4aac-b6c3-fd96-b586681f8ade"], "h6925c76bg831bg4ea9ga4efg220835684814": ["If anyone has me concerned, it's you. You haven't exactly been open about yourself.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "546670f3-fa7c-85c4-4d6b-62e051a7b798"], "h14c8e21fgd33bg4636g9b41g187c773a9a34": ["I think I've been more than candid - you know about my faith, for one thing.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "62ebb8bd-446a-2aca-7ab8-411f8692ea79"], "h00f7f0d5gada8g4b99g93c2gc3e3cee72c52": ["Either way, be careful. You never know what lengths someone might take to solve this little problem of ours.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "82065476-6419-03a2-ae22-8bcf2d4aa688"], "h50d31040gf819g4fecg93fcg11a6da0912de": ["I have my reasons - they're nothing for you to be concerned about.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "3cfa18ca-f836-8c4f-d6d6-a1c9234ef68c"], "hac13e355g9209g44e1g93d7gaeb93781cf4f": ["I'd be careful with Wyll.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "614f4f26-ad90-8493-ef9a-a4e74ff8ba51"], "hf4852ac6gaa69g4b09g9b71g3f1ae6dd8e2b": ["You don't trust Wyll?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "13b4a9f5-4fb3-2d37-3a42-bf671b095e5c"], "hd3217ac2g104fg4a64g99f1g62dacc8ee2d9": ["Heroic types can be brittle, I find. Better to trust someone with greater flexibility.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "c81fa41b-5af2-ad60-855b-9d7b3848c544"], "hdc4375f0g5cd5g423dga525gff00b098ede3": ["I'd be careful with Astarion.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "98bac20e-8006-bcaa-baa9-3c68d981bb1f"], "hdbba2a10gbde1g4bcag8119g6635bc0ead9f": ["You don't trust Astarion?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "c25946d3-b739-81b8-fb33-d00b4f280efc"], "hf74eb31eg69c6g47d1g85d5g68b6fc7d4846": ["Trust is a rare currency. Not sure I'd spend it on someone who drew a knife on me moments after I met them.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "eb5867d2-17a4-f06c-007d-90fcbceaa6f6"], "h768029b4g0d55g4890gb66bg649c9ae014c8": ["I'd be careful with Gale.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "c3502a0e-8a4a-d702-490d-84c660019289"], "h63bab38cge85bg4c39gafd5g4e6f103fc5e4": ["You don't trust Gale?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "8cf1c8f5-a410-ef82-5857-a62b3e20c4cd"], "he5ed3103g0313g429eg8174g7c9d4513d39a": ["He's a wizard. All they care about is power.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "58b6ec03-50cc-a0da-69dc-fbe14ca281c4"], "h7a2801b8g241ag4c12g9516gff1892fc0ae9": ["I'd be careful with who you confide in.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "f0229b01-6d8c-5d7a-b7be-f343f3d34226"], "hd77fe826g3b8eg4916g95fdg13b234311f07": ["You don't trust our companions?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "2e666254-9ddb-68f5-ce04-3b8106c69939"], "h0f57252agb556g45f3g839ag1cd62da3af3c": ["Well, what do we <i>really </i>know about them...?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "a6343988-946c-e160-6d10-2020d1f51304"], "h83e489f9g422cg4c9bg8de0g7e68f17fd2fa": ["You strike me as the reliable sort, but are you sure this is a good idea?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "d419a52e-f818-2a0b-9ac5-131eb60d273c"], "hbd925484g8c8cg40eeg9f57gd91fd59667a5": ["I'm not sure this is a good idea.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "6bcdad7f-bd29-ec80-5262-7f383146dbb4"], "hf5545998gcd72g402bgbe03g4cac899b2743": ["Sure <i>what </i>is a good idea?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "7dfa9b22-6c57-fdac-f5d9-336ad2abbc6f"], "h856d6d6eg533ag47b2g8b78g1005c1bb2687": ["There are lit fuses in our heads. Sooner or later, they're going to blow.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "6af79471-ec99-9840-f35c-9f3cdc055374"], "h97f148d6gf111g4891gb0fcgb8875d4a75ae": ["Each hour that passes, the thing inside us grows. We need to find a healer. Let's wake up at first light.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "313a5b8e-5850-f4a5-f1fa-64dcf9f9d1c2"], "hdcd5c81cgfe11g45d9ga141g460e01cbf7d3": ["Agreed. Our top priority, as far as I'm concerned.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "461194a9-d841-469c-8ff2-527a7b0c4ec5"], "heabe322ag0632g4fd7gb18ag7f1718149a01": ["Maybe we will get lucky. We're overdue some good fortune.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "a7b2ed1b-cff8-1745-55da-12c66b6053e3"], "h13150436g1097g4d8ag805dg308bd6b2a98d": ["Fine. But it won't be easy, searching this wilderness.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "e24b2eb7-6d52-f964-c400-240c186d3db1"], "h59a8915cga5bbg4b11g9e47g2b2a16904b27": ["Maybe. But we might get lucky. We're overdue some good fortune.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "120a33ea-6a49-39f7-1398-f7abe103d2ba"], "h57c8ced0g0256g4cd8g8297g041ccc368394": ["This is unfamiliar territory. Rushing will only land us in more trouble than we can handle.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "ac73465e-61bf-8b82-8c35-09034b85603b"], "h42194e21gc591g4437g82c7ge7a94823613a": ["That sort of danger - I'm fine with. I can <i>fight </i>it.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "8e45a3e0-452b-bda4-4ee3-ce5d0768d648"], "hb1f081e2ge257g4810g87d8g6d9d5b795192": ["Relax. This camp seems safe from threats.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "c224c980-98a0-1bcc-4343-84c1ff968b5a"], "hb2a495bdg21c4g4ac7g823dg93ddf5a80daa": ["Outside threats, perhaps.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "2a491503-1724-4e6e-35a9-b5a87eaad691"], "h2ddde6c8g8ed0g4504gb917ga72474393af6": ["Don't fret. We need some rest.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "56f6dc70-8466-b7f4-8ad4-b04c690f58c4"], "h0f0784afgb32ag4312g9ceag089bd2316cbe": ["Fine. But not for too long.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "4ecfad9a-f9ab-39ab-3d00-16a21efcf4ef"], "hef956f91ga11ag4219gb24fg0d428c748095": ["Don't question me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "c533fcc0-7173-b819-7ba9-5efe790ea01b"], "hc8b7dff2g3dceg4fb8gac61g55370cd38a92": ["Spare me the petty tyrant routine - you're better than that.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "f60adf6f-19f8-d4c3-00bc-b04030e8b2ac"], "h423eb0ddg04eeg4e3bga2a0g2186a8f528d3": ["You should get some rest. We've got hard times ahead.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "b3520795-82bc-b77d-712e-55621391c464"], "h391ef41bgff0eg4115g8e7dg797be0bb578e": ["Oh, it's going to be like that? I love strong men.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "ed3c3acc-6b1d-c940-f4de-0d3eda2bec7e"], "hbf57fa18ga815g4dc9ga1a5g1ecac4b8c2b5": ["Oh, it's going to be like that? I love strong women.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "ed3c3acc-6b1d-c940-f4de-0d3eda2bec7e"], "h4e161938ge8f2g4065g81f1ga52347343c51": ["They make the best servants.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "eac29dc9-c5c4-c7f9-c248-755d6f5c8d8e"], "h4947fd8bga93ag4a9fga020g9157776b311c": ["Get some rest. We move at dawn.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night1_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "ad81c11f-8822-c13c-1943-657d4c4b206c"]}